{
  "texts": [
    "PCG signals, spectrograms, and deep learning methods have all been used in recent research as well 14, 15.",
    "This study presents a novel approach for detecting heart disease using audio signals to optimize the detection technique.",
    "The schematic in Fig. 1 illustrates the proposed technique in a block diagram format.",
    "The proposed methodology encompasses a series of sequential stages: data acquisition, data augmentation, data pre-processing, feature extraction, feature normalization, model selection, model implementation, and result prediction.",
    "This study aims to enhance the reliability of the comparative analyses conducted in previous studies 8, 9."
  ]
}